Nintendo Tank Console Game with Sound using SFML lib

How to Play – Nintendo Tank (Console)

Goal
    Destroy all enemy tanks to win.
    If your tank is hit → Game Over.

Controls
    W → Move Up
    S → Move Down
    A → Move Left
    D → Move Right
    F → Fire in the last moved direction
    Q → Quit the game

Symbols
    P → Player tank
    E → Enemy tank
    * → Bullet
    . → Empty space

Win / Lose
    Win: All enemies destroyed
    Lose: Enemy bullet hits you